WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.013 --> 00:00:02.853
Good evening, everybody.

00:00:02.853 --> 00:00:05.680
Thank you for joining us again tonight.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:07.669
I have my sweetheart with me tonight.

00:00:07.669 --> 00:00:19.960
I told her we will go ahead and pray and seek the Lord to see what He has for us tonight concerning our nation.

00:00:19.960 --> 00:00:28.889
Today, when I was driving around and doing errands, I saw in the spirit a headline in the New York Times.

00:00:30.311 --> 00:00:35.200
The caption in bold letters said, 'Terror in Manhattan.

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:37.748
' Thank you, son.

00:00:37.748 --> 00:00:40.320
'Terror in Manhattan.

00:00:40.320 --> 00:00:47.039
' In the picture, I saw a lot of smoke and a building.

00:00:57.607 --> 00:01:01.039
I saw 'Terror in Manhattan' in bold on the front of this newspaper, and below it, 'Terror strikes again in America.

00:01:01.039 --> 00:01:03.1000
' Then it had the article of what happened.

00:01:32.160 --> 00:01:32.560
As I was praying—I guess we're just going to jump right into this to save you time—I saw an umbrella with beautiful colors; it was a protection.

00:01:56.079 --> 00:02:04.240
But because of choices that were made, this umbrella had holes all in it.

00:02:06.090 --> 00:02:12.800
Decisions being made over the years caused the holes to get bigger and bigger.

00:02:14.846 --> 00:02:28.140
The more the umbrella was covering over America, the more people were holding it and were excited to have it because it blocked the storms and the plan of the enemy.

00:02:28.140 --> 00:02:31.840
This umbrella was a covering.

00:02:32.276 --> 00:02:40.699
As American citizens or people around the world, you have this prayer covering from the churches.

00:02:40.699 --> 00:02:55.599
But as you make decisions against God's word, against God's plan, and against what God originally wanted for us, you cause holes in your umbrella.

00:02:56.319 --> 00:03:04.959
We repent, and the covering is still there, but there were holes in it because of those decisions.

00:03:05.309 --> 00:03:20.700
I saw these holes that were seemingly really small at the beginning, like pinholes, but over the course of time, the holes got larger and larger until the umbrella was no longer there.

00:03:21.030 --> 00:03:33.760
The Lord showed me the prayer covering of a home and the importance of the male being the head of the household.

00:03:34.069 --> 00:03:40.766
The man brings a covering over it, and the wife provides a prayer covering, too.

00:03:40.766 --> 00:03:45.897
There is so much importance in a man leading his family.

00:03:53.160 --> 00:04:08.390
The Lord was showing me the importance of righteous men in the household rising up and being what God has called you to be: lead your family, take them to church, pray with your kids, and pray with your wife.

00:04:08.390 --> 00:04:10.126
Be a godly spouse.

00:04:10.594 --> 00:04:14.920
Speak good things over your children and your wife.

00:04:14.920 --> 00:04:20.320
Bless your children and your wife spiritually, physically, and financially.

00:04:20.320 --> 00:04:24.720
Whatever you can do, you be that head.

00:04:25.648 --> 00:04:50.800
I saw that as America goes, as the church goes, and as big decisions go, that covering—no matter how much we prayed and asked God to cover things—the more unbiblical decisions were made, like those made in New York by the mayor, the more it caused holes.

00:04:56.267 --> 00:05:01.874
I saw a terror attack, and the Lord said, 'Do you see the power of prayer, Brandon?

00:05:01.874 --> 00:05:02.937
What it does?

00:05:02.937 --> 00:05:04.416
It brings that covering.

00:05:04.416 --> 00:05:08.740
But because you make unrighteous decisions, you open the door for the enemy.

00:05:08.740 --> 00:05:11.759
' I said, 'Lord, I need scriptures.

00:05:11.759 --> 00:05:18.720
' He brought up Job and other scriptures that Diana wrote down.

00:05:26.589 --> 00:05:42.978
The devil said, 'You've put a hedge around Job and I'm not able to touch it,' but if you remove that hedge, what Job feared the most came on him.

00:05:42.978 --> 00:05:49.759
He opened the door through fear; fear tolerated, faith contaminated.

00:05:50.079 --> 00:05:57.210
As he was making sacrifices out of fear for his children and acting out of fear, he opened the door for it.

00:06:02.270 --> 00:06:11.600
Now, when we have a church covering and you keep praying over it, He showed me the thorns.

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:24.120
Not Hosea, I believe it was in Ezekiel—whoever breaks a hedge, the serpent will bite him.

00:06:24.120 --> 00:06:34.080
Okay, that's Ecclesiastes 10:8: 'Whoever breaks a hedge, a serpent will bite him.

00:06:34.080 --> 00:06:46.880
' As you break the hedge and that umbrella of covering, it allows the enemy to come in and kill, steal, and destroy.

00:06:49.920 --> 00:07:00.720
We have authority, but if you keep making ungodly decisions, and He says, 'I want you to live righteously,' but you are sleeping around while claiming to be a praying Christian, you are opening the door.

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:05.039
That covering gets holes in it because you are allowing sin in.

00:07:05.039 --> 00:07:13.572
That is what the Lord was showing me today: the covering of prayer over America as we keep making these bad decisions.

00:07:29.860 --> 00:07:30.040
That's what He keeps talking about in 1 Corinthians 5:5.

00:07:30.040 --> 00:07:35.234
It is not His will for any of us to perish.

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:53.680
Ladies and gentlemen, you think because you go through a hard time for a season, that is God's judgment.

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:58.560
True judgment is separation from God for eternity.

00:07:58.560 --> 00:08:02.756
It's not the day-to-day hard times.

00:08:09.028 --> 00:08:12.787
The way the Lord kept showing me was, 'That is not judgment, Brandon.

00:08:12.787 --> 00:08:18.296
True judgment is whenever you are going to hell forever and there is no returning.

00:08:18.296 --> 00:08:25.897
It's the point where there is no turning back; you are in hell forever.

00:08:25.897 --> 00:08:37.257
' The moment you take your last breath and you do not have Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior, if you are not a born-again Christian, that is true judgment.

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:48.251
But having a shaking to awaken people—like what I have seen coming—they will all say, 'This is judgment.

00:08:48.251 --> 00:08:53.173
God's mad,' and they will call it an Ichabod.

00:08:53.173 --> 00:08:56.253
'God has departed from America.

00:08:56.253 --> 00:09:01.820
' No, it is people making poor choices and voting unwisely.

00:09:01.820 --> 00:09:07.392
They keep thinking they can do these things without repercussions.

00:09:09.023 --> 00:09:10.925
I am trying to tell you what I keep seeing.

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:17.530
When I saw the headlines in the paper, I said, 'Oh Lord.

00:09:17.530 --> 00:09:22.959
' He said, 'Brandon, do you see the importance of a choice?

00:09:22.959 --> 00:09:27.909
Do you see the importance of the prayer covering that you bring over your family?

00:09:27.909 --> 00:09:37.290
' That covers you; you have the authority to pray that your family is always in the right place at the right time.

00:09:37.290 --> 00:09:39.787
But I am talking about as a city as a whole.

00:09:39.787 --> 00:09:47.840
You keep making poor choices and voting in ways that allow the enemy to get a stronghold in an area.

00:09:52.027 --> 00:09:55.820
That is why I was praying over these things today.

00:09:55.820 --> 00:10:06.092
People might say, 'Brandon, you're being too harsh,' but I am just telling you what I am praying over today.

00:10:11.940 --> 00:10:13.390
It is a little raw, but this is what I am seeing in the headlines.

00:10:13.390 --> 00:10:17.519
I saw a great shaking coming again.

00:10:19.173 --> 00:10:23.760
I keep seeing these things, and quite frankly, it is very sobering.

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:32.960
I even told her, "I could feel such a shifting last night," praying over President Trump and the things I saw.

00:10:34.178 --> 00:10:46.240
I'm going to go over some of that, but I was just trying to give you an update of what we saw today as I'm praying.

00:10:47.876 --> 00:10:49.227
I want to go over this.

00:10:49.227 --> 00:10:59.480
Remember yesterday, we saw a lot about drones last night and the night before.

00:10:59.480 --> 00:11:10.079
We kept seeing drones in the sky, and I saw a new wave of terror activity in America using drones from Amazon strapped with explosive devices.

00:11:10.470 --> 00:11:27.380
I thought that was interesting because I never see that; I always see them using vans, trucks, or semis, and the Lord keeps telling me to pray over this, but now I'm seeing drones more.

00:11:27.380 --> 00:11:37.013
As I've been seeing all these things about drones and praying over New Year's Eve and the Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade, Braden stumbled upon this.

00:11:37.013 --> 00:11:39.960
I'll let you watch this.

00:11:57.040 --> 00:11:57.253
This is not a coincidence; this is how we're being led on this channel.

00:12:05.200 --> 00:12:05.400
I think it's very interesting what's being said.

00:12:05.400 --> 00:12:07.691
Do you have it ready?

00:12:07.691 --> 00:12:10.559
This is Fox News.

00:12:24.660 --> 00:12:28.507
It's not a coincidence what we've been hearing because they're talking about it, and the Trump administration is already preparing for it—$500 million and doing all the things they can to combat what they believe are credible threats.

00:12:28.507 --> 00:12:32.445
We're getting this by the spirit of God.

00:12:41.380 --> 00:12:41.690
This news article comes out two days later after we prayed about it.

00:12:41.690 --> 00:12:47.680
I thought, "Are they listening to our webcast?

00:12:47.680 --> 00:12:52.648
Are these news reporters watching us?

00:12:52.648 --> 00:12:57.989
" I don't believe they are, but they could be.

00:12:57.989 --> 00:13:02.240
Wouldn't it be neat if Fox News was watching?

00:13:02.240 --> 00:13:05.138
Maybe they'll get saved if they're not.

00:13:14.220 --> 00:13:14.996
I think it's interesting that we are praying over these things and it's coming up in the news.

00:13:17.538 --> 00:13:19.600
This is exactly the assignment the Lord told us about, even concerning New Year's Eve.

00:13:19.600 --> 00:13:42.697
When I saw the drone coming in, the Lord said this is related to Ukraine and black swan events—major events to shake New York as we see the deadline of the Trump administration saying we want a deal done on Ukraine concerning the Russia war.

00:13:42.697 --> 00:13:49.319
He was saying they want that done by Thanksgiving.

00:13:49.319 --> 00:14:01.223
As we see this, I've seen an escalation because Zelensky was looking at Macron and was like, "What do I do?

00:14:01.223 --> 00:14:11.600
" He didn't know what to do, and they were trying to come up—and this is what I saw in the spirit.

00:14:11.600 --> 00:14:27.470
They wanted the war to keep going because of the suits; I saw these businessmen in suits who were funding it and wanted the war to keep going.

00:14:35.631 --> 00:14:36.063
The other part was the tunnels underneath Rome.

00:14:42.520 --> 00:14:42.880
I saw old flaming torches lighting the tunnels in Rome underneath the Vatican.

00:14:42.880 --> 00:14:46.171
I saw there were tunnels and they were very old.

00:14:52.079 --> 00:14:52.359
These tunnels looked like they could have been hundreds of years old, winding deep underground.

00:14:52.359 --> 00:14:56.000
They were a representation of something the Lord said was dark.

00:14:58.200 --> 00:14:59.100
I saw these—like I said, it was not electric.

00:15:01.617 --> 00:15:08.764
It was torches lit on fire like old caves, with a wrap around them in a holder in a tunnel.

00:15:08.764 --> 00:15:23.509
I try not to talk about this because it's controversial, but I saw what I saw and the Lord was telling me.

00:15:31.938 --> 00:15:32.213
It was right after we prayed about sex trafficking that I saw tunnels, and I thought, "That's dark.

00:15:32.213 --> 00:15:41.600
" Braden showed this to me today about President Trump.

00:15:44.079 --> 00:15:48.738
President Trump says America is finding its way back to church and to God.

00:15:48.738 --> 00:15:54.319
He says more people are praying, churches are coming back, and religion is coming back to America.

00:15:57.280 --> 00:16:01.749
To me, that's a big deal.

00:16:01.759 --> 00:16:08.959
I was excited, thinking that's exactly what we want for a god-fearing administration.

00:16:17.474 --> 00:16:21.359
We need a president who brings prayer back.

00:16:21.786 --> 00:16:31.519
People are praying more than ever before.

00:16:37.897 --> 00:16:51.493
I know what the Lord showed me: that he would be radically born again, baptized in the Holy Ghost and fire, and speaking in tongues.

00:16:51.827 --> 00:16:55.039
There would be a major move of God on his heart.

00:17:01.839 --> 00:17:11.120
He's more Christian, in terms of standing for biblical basis things, than any administration has been since I was a kid—maybe Ronald Reagan.

00:17:15.800 --> 00:17:16.346
I'm excited to see him walking with his wife.

00:17:17.439 --> 00:17:22.469
I'm praying over their marriage, their children, and these things.

00:17:30.186 --> 00:17:30.453
Let's go to what we saw last night.

00:17:37.733 --> 00:17:44.907
I saw him going to the Winter Olympics, and I saw an octopus.

00:17:45.280 --> 00:18:00.640
This demonic octopus came up before me in Europe, and it was trying to cause a smoke screen so that I couldn't see the plans and plots concerning his life.

00:18:10.640 --> 00:18:10.983
The octopus spoke to me and said, "I'm not moving," but I said, "You are moving.

00:18:10.983 --> 00:18:20.600
You've got to move out of the way, and you don't have a choice.

00:18:20.600 --> 00:18:30.504
" As I started to attack that and tell it to move, it let out ink—a black cloud that flooded my viewing area.

00:18:30.808 --> 00:18:35.064
I got quiet, wondering what to do as I'd never come across this before.

00:18:35.280 --> 00:18:37.200
The Lord said, "Brandon, go up higher.

00:18:37.200 --> 00:18:38.799
You've got to go over it.

00:18:38.799 --> 00:18:41.371
Come up higher like an eagle and see over it.

00:18:43.611 --> 00:18:54.400
" I started praying in the spirit, and he said, "I'm not going to show all of it because it would bring danger to you.

00:18:54.400 --> 00:18:58.680
" So he said, I'll show you in part.

00:18:58.680 --> 00:19:05.359
So I saw, I go up higher, and then I saw France again and I saw a train station.

00:19:05.359 --> 00:19:13.039
Then I saw pastries, a coffee shop, and baguettes, and croissants.

00:19:15.790 --> 00:19:22.000
And I saw tables outside where it was like a restaurant, they could sit outside and enjoy their meal.

00:19:25.980 --> 00:19:26.240
The Lord was showing me terrorist attacks concerning France.

00:19:34.023 --> 00:19:34.274
He said, This does not only have to do with America, but this is concerning Europe.

00:19:47.520 --> 00:19:47.880
So, that is what we were praying into last night.

00:19:50.200 --> 00:19:52.620
I saw about Europe and I saw Germany, France, and England.

00:19:52.620 --> 00:20:19.180
That is when I saw the scorpion again and I saw the king of England like the scorpion coming out and looking at Canada and these places.

00:20:19.180 --> 00:20:36.050
I thought that was interesting because people talked about the scorpion and what it represents and the horoscopes and all that stuff, which I do not look at any of that trash.

00:20:38.000 --> 00:20:59.840
But I think it is interesting because of the demonic ties to what the Lord is trying to say to me because of Scorpio or whatever they were trying to say.

00:20:59.840 --> 00:21:03.020
But the Lord is not using horoscopes.

00:21:03.020 --> 00:21:06.194
God is not doing that.

00:21:09.337 --> 00:21:14.240
I am trying to tell you all that the devil latches onto that demonic stuff because that is him.

00:21:14.240 --> 00:21:17.120
He is the author of confusion, demonic, evil stuff.

00:21:17.120 --> 00:21:19.391
So, I thought that was interesting.

00:21:26.592 --> 00:21:28.680
What were you going to say?

00:21:32.266 --> 00:21:35.360
I was trying to help you.

00:21:38.799 --> 00:21:39.039
You saw the escalator in the center.

00:21:39.039 --> 00:21:40.490
You saw malls.

00:21:40.490 --> 00:21:42.213
Praying over malls.

00:21:56.068 --> 00:21:56.559
I saw the center of malls and I heard like fish in a barrel.

00:21:56.559 --> 00:22:03.874
They were like fish in a barrel because they were looking and there was nowhere for them to run.

00:22:22.190 --> 00:22:37.200
It takes them too long to get away and they had a plan using mass shootings and things like that in malls during the holiday season, not just in America.

00:22:37.200 --> 00:22:42.091
This was concerning Rome, Italy, all over the place.

00:22:42.091 --> 00:22:43.488
And the Lord said, Pray over this.

00:22:44.224 --> 00:22:51.840
I heard them talking; they are like fish in a barrel.

00:22:52.302 --> 00:23:02.720
Then I saw something to do with the key word in the underground chats about stocking hats.

00:23:03.200 --> 00:23:13.229
Holiday hats, Christmas hats, Christmas elves, and it was something about the Santa Claus hats.

00:23:13.539 --> 00:23:21.440
I thought that was interesting because I saw underground chatter again.

00:23:22.453 --> 00:23:25.173
We prayed over all that last night.

00:23:25.404 --> 00:23:34.754
I felt like we had a lot, like I told you all, I feel like we are icebreakers every single time.

00:23:34.754 --> 00:23:37.280
I feel like we just plow right through.

00:23:37.280 --> 00:23:48.140
And I believe every time we come together and we pray like this, we are just plowing through that spiritual, demonic ice, and we are taking things down.

00:23:48.140 --> 00:23:58.000
But like I said, when it comes to New York in some of these areas, I pray for the people to have wisdom where they are.

00:24:08.860 --> 00:24:11.851
I am trying to tell you all that there are holes in their umbrella.

00:24:16.824 --> 00:24:16.992
That is what I keep saying.

00:24:16.992 --> 00:24:21.680
This prayer covering, there are holes in the umbrella of New York.

00:24:31.419 --> 00:24:31.840
And that is what the Lord said, Brandon, do you see that?

00:24:42.680 --> 00:24:43.280
I said, Yes, I do.

00:24:49.808 --> 00:24:50.112
I see it, Lord.

00:24:50.416 --> 00:24:52.987
I am asking for grace and mercy.

00:24:59.745 --> 00:25:05.072
I am asking, Father, that the people that are there, there would be a covering over them because I heard terror in Manhattan.

00:25:06.063 --> 00:25:10.640
It was in the New York Times: Terror strikes again in America.

00:25:25.896 --> 00:25:26.192
And I thought, Oh, this is heavy.

00:25:26.192 --> 00:25:39.679
As it is with us, we just keep praying over things, but I try to keep you up to date.

00:25:39.679 --> 00:25:41.716
You saw a battle plan.

00:25:41.716 --> 00:25:44.060
I saw a battle plan.

00:25:47.440 --> 00:25:49.300
It was on a table.

00:25:55.857 --> 00:25:56.266
It looked like a table, but these people in the terrorist organizations were strategizing.

00:26:03.520 --> 00:26:03.780
I saw the Washington Monument.

00:26:10.845 --> 00:26:11.303
I saw these areas and they had them on a map.

00:26:13.859 --> 00:26:17.279
But it was interesting that they were all like real-life plastic toys.

00:26:28.284 --> 00:26:38.219
It was a model of the White House and they had it all set up looking at each individual thing of where it was on this table almost like Legos.

00:26:43.787 --> 00:26:44.440
A 3D model.

00:26:44.440 --> 00:26:45.747
Yes.

00:26:45.747 --> 00:27:06.720
But then they had one and it was over San Francisco and the Golden Gate Bridge was a part of it.

00:27:06.720 --> 00:27:37.093
I could see the bridge but it looked like little plastic models, maybe 3D printouts, Legos, or whatever it was, but they had it on a table and they were strategizing concerning the Fourth of July.

00:27:49.989 --> 00:27:58.880
I went to the 4th of July, and it was over the 250th anniversary, and the Lord allowed me to look into this and he said, Pray into the plans concerning it.

00:28:09.371 --> 00:28:12.850
It is not the day.

00:28:12.850 --> 00:28:17.566
This is a Pearl Harbor experience to catch you by surprise.

00:28:24.640 --> 00:28:24.987
He said, Similar to October 7th to catch you by surprise.

00:28:30.489 --> 00:28:51.280
He kept saying to expect the unexpected concerning major events in the spirit realm, plots, and so they had this table and they had every single one of something that was important to us as Americans as a model.

00:28:56.493 --> 00:28:56.720
But the Lord was circling 250 years of American history in April.

00:28:56.720 --> 00:28:58.448
Pray over April 13th.

00:28:58.736 --> 00:29:04.352
It was highlighted before me and he talked about Easter.

00:29:04.352 --> 00:29:10.045
Orthodox Easter is the 14th, I believe, or the 13th, the day after.

00:29:10.045 --> 00:29:12.068
But he highlighted the Jewish Holocaust.

00:29:12.068 --> 00:29:18.228
Holocaust Remembrance Day is on Monday, April 13th, 2026.

00:29:20.571 --> 00:29:22.960
I was seeing that day highlighted and it was circled.

00:29:22.960 --> 00:29:27.139
He said, Pray over that day.

00:29:33.800 --> 00:29:33.1000
I saw that and I thought, Well, that is a very sad day.

00:29:37.412 --> 00:29:37.786
It is Holocaust Remembrance Day.

00:29:37.786 --> 00:29:39.759
Why April 13th?

00:29:45.417 --> 00:29:47.760
After I went from April, it went clear to July, and he said, Pray over these time frames.

00:29:47.760 --> 00:29:53.973
Black swan events, major, and he kept talking about Pearl Harbor event, the Red Dawn experience, the enemy within.

00:29:53.973 --> 00:29:56.320
That table was really planned out.

00:29:56.320 --> 00:30:18.565
It is like taking graphics and everything, but it was like Lego things so they had a visual, and he was taking a teaching stick and he was pointing to each one, and they were talking about how they could do things and strategizing.

00:30:29.141 --> 00:30:29.388
I thought that was kind of interesting.

00:30:29.388 --> 00:30:32.560
Some of the things I see are metaphors.

00:30:32.560 --> 00:30:38.343
They are symbolic, like Lily, that young girl Diana.

00:30:38.343 --> 00:30:41.983
You said she lives in Australia.

00:30:41.983 --> 00:30:45.725
It was not about a real Lily.

00:30:45.725 --> 00:30:51.332
It was a fragrance, but it was about her name.

00:30:53.949 --> 00:31:01.646
I truly believe after we have prayed over that, that is who we are praying for that God would give a supernatural song to.

00:31:14.399 --> 00:31:14.759
It is the way the Lord shows with visions and dreams.

00:31:14.759 --> 00:31:21.264
A lot of times it is symbolic, but sometimes it is just black and white.

00:31:21.264 --> 00:31:31.307
Diana has a lot of cool dreams and prophetic things, and a lot of times it is symbolic.

00:31:31.307 --> 00:31:34.823
Good morning, America.

00:31:47.280 --> 00:31:47.760
I believe it has to do with the sun coming up and the show concerning the Olympics.

00:31:47.760 --> 00:31:52.080
Yes, it was concerning the Olympic Village.

00:31:52.080 --> 00:32:05.177
There's something about praying over the Olympics with Good Morning America, and that was the same thing with praying over President Trump if he ends up going to the Olympics.

